<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Visa Application Form</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="header">
        <div class="heading">
            <h1>VISA APPLICATION FORM</h1>
            <p>Please fill in the form completely and correctly in BLOCK LETTERS.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="photo-box">
            <p>PHOTO</p>
            (35mm x 45mm)<br>
            (White Background)
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="top-section">
        <div class="official">
            <div class="title">FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY</div>
            <table>
                <tr>
                    <td>Application No.</td>
                    <td>___________________________</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Date of Application</td>
                    <td>___________________________</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Visa Category</td>
                    <td>___________________________</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td>Received By</td>
                    <td>___________________________</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="visa-type">
            <h3>Type of Visa Applied For <span>(Please tick one)</span></h3>
            <div class="options">
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Tourist / Visitor</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Business</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Transit</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Student</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Work</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Family Visit</label>
                <label><input type="checkbox"> Medical</label>
                <label style="width: 100%;"><input type="checkbox"> Others (Please specify) ___________________</label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-heading">1. PERSONAL INFORMATION</div>
    <table class="form-table">
        <tr>
            <td colspan="2" style="width: 60%;">
                <label>1.1 Full Name <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(as in passport)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td style="width: 40%;">
                <label>1.2 Date of Birth <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(DD/MM/YYYY)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>1.3 Gender</label>
                <div class="inline">
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Male</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Female</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Other</label>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td>
                <label>1.4 Place of Birth</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td>
                <label>1.5 Nationality</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>1.6 Marital Status</label>
                <div class="inline">
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Single</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Married</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Divorced</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Widowed</label>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td colspan="2">
                <label>1.7 Mother's Full Name</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td colspan="3">
                <label>1.8 Father's Full Name</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>1.9 Passport Number</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td>
                <label>1.10 Date of Issue <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(DD/MM/YYYY)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td>
                <label>1.11 Date of Expiry <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(DD/MM/YYYY)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>1.12 Place of Issue</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td colspan="2">
                <label>1.13 National ID Number <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(if any)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>1.14 Occupation</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td colspan="2">
                <label>1.15 Employer / Business Name</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td colspan="3">
                <label>1.16 Employer / Business Address</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>1.17 Phone Number</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td>
                <label>1.18 Email Address</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td>
                <label>1.19 Alternate Contact Number</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="section-heading">2. TRAVEL INFORMATION</div>
    <table class="form-table">
        <tr>
            <td colspan="3">
                <label>2.1 Purpose of Visit</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 35%;">
                <label>2.2 Date of Arrival <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(DD/MM/YYYY)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td style="width: 35%;">
                <label>2.3 Date of Departure <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(DD/MM/YYYY)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
            <td style="width: 30%;">
                <label>2.4 Port of Entry</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td colspan="3">
                <label>2.5 Address in the Country of Visit</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td colspan="3">
                <label>2.6 Name & Address of Contact Person / Organization in the Country of Visit</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>2.7 Will you be accompanied by anyone?</label>
                <div class="inline" style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Yes</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> No</label>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td colspan="2">
                <label>2.8 If yes, please provide details</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="section-heading">3. PREVIOUS TRAVEL INFORMATION</div>
    <table class="form-table">
        <tr>
            <td style="width: 50%;">
                <label>3.1 Have you ever visited this country before?</label>
                <div class="inline">
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Yes</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> No</label>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td style="width: 50%;">
                <label>3.2 If yes, last visit date <span style="font-weight: normal; color: #555;">(DD/MM/YYYY)</span></label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>
                <label>3.3 Have you ever been refused a visa for this country or any other country?</label>
                <div class="inline">
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> Yes</label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox"> No</label>
                </div>
            </td>
            <td>
                <label>3.4 If yes, please provide details</label>
                <input type="text">
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="section-heading">4. DECLARATION</div>
    <table class="form-table">
        <tr>
            <td class="declaration-text">
                I hereby declare that the information given above is true, complete and correct to the best of my knowledge and belief. I understand that any false information may lead to the refusal of my application or cancellation of visa.
                
                <div class="signature-row">
                    <div>Date: ________________________</div>
                    <div>Applicant's Signature: ________________________</div>
                </div>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </table>

    <div class="footer-note">
        <div class="note-title">
            <strong>NOTE:</strong>
            <p>Please attach the following documents with your application:</p>
        </div>
        <ul class="doc-list">
            <li>Valid Passport</li>
            <li>Proof of Accommodation</li>
            <li>Passport Size Photograph</li>
            <li>Financial Proof</li>
            <li>Travel Itinerary / Flight Booking</li>
            <li>Any other supporting documents</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
